{"step_by_step_thinking": "According to the relevant documents, the blade-/plate-form implant has been shown to be successful under three different types of integration: fibrous integration, fibro-osseous integration, and osseous integration. Fibro-osseous integration is a combination of thinly defined fibrous connection with 22% or less direct bone contact with the implant.
